<plot>Ravi Varma is a single eligible bachelor. He meets with Aarti Mathur, and both are attracted to each other. The problem is that Ravi is unable to express his love and attraction for Aarti, and Aarti unsure of Ravi's intentions, is unsure of his feelings for her. Soon Aarti's marriage is arranged, and it is then Ravi must decide to speak out his feelings or let Aarti's marriage take place, and maintain his silence.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?168280</url></doc>
